CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 26, 1953, pg. 19, reads: "Nonagenarian - Clifton Davidson was greeted Saturday, Sept. 19, by Mrs. Alberta Ham, left, and the Rev. Grover F. Nelson, right, on the occasion of his ninety-fourth birthday. Mr. Davidson lives at the Aged Ministers and Laymen's Home.  Mrs. Ham and the Rev. Mr. Nelson are board members of the home. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alberta Ham and Rev. Grover F. Nelson, leaning over Clifton Davidson on his ninety-fourth birthday, in Aged Ministers and Laymen's Home
